63. Future high-resolution X-ray missions, e.g. Athena and\nXRISM, will test them by resolving different spectral components.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2022 16:03:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
