ble rate of dispersal outflows and\nsupernovae (approximately one every 50 years), which may be important for the\nenergy budget of the Interstellar Medium and the link between dispersal\noutflows and high-mass star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2022 19:35:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
