 equations coming from using the monosome\n(single ribosome) and polysome (arbitrary number) ribo-seq profiles enable us\nto determine all the kinetic rates in terms of the experimentally accessible\nmRNA degradation rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 10:49:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-29"}
