oor environment. The proposed system is\nreleased open-source with an extensive dataset including ToF and gray-scale\ncamera data, coupled with UAV position ground truth from motion capture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 12:33:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-29"}
