atively smooth and delayed compared\nto an instantaneous feeding prescription. While the reduction of accretion due\nto feedback is present in both accretion disc and instantaneous feeding\nsimulations, a clear central cavity appears only in accretion disc runs -\nhinting that a less volatile accretion phase could have a greater impact on the\nsurrounding gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 14:38:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-29"}
